    "Only 37 items remained after removing the duplicates.",
    "According to the total number of publications appearing in various journals, Table 2 lists the top three reliable references.",
    "Big Data & Society has published most research articles examining AI's role in developing digital marketing content.",
    "Big Data & Society has twice as many journal papers from the top two journals in their field, ArXiv Preprint and Developing Digital Marketing.",
    "In addition, the H-index and I10-index were used to compare the three most relevant sources to determine which one was the most important."
